{"name":"For to Breathe Like Unto a Dragon","permission":{"default":0,"5OXcsyHbucZmXIwZ":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":"<p>With this spell, the caster spits a stream of fire at his target. If the fire is not Dodged, it inflicts 1D8 points of heat damage. Armour Points are effective against this damage and it counts as both magickal and fire damage.</p>","skill":"0","area":0,"charm":false,"concentration":false,"distant":false,"duration":0,"eyeContact":false,"instant":true,"magnitude":1,"progressive":false,"ranged":true,"resist":"Dodge","touch":false,"trigger":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"4Ona3YM53EWLUIrm"}
{"name":"For to Cause the Conflagration of a Blade","permission":{"default":0,"5OXcsyHbucZmXIwZ":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":"<p>For the Duration, the target weapon will deal 1D10 magickal fire damage on top of its normal damage. A weapon under the effects of For to Cause the Conflagration of a Blade cannot benefit from For to Sharpen a Blade.</p>","skill":"0","area":0,"charm":false,"concentration":false,"distant":false,"duration":5,"eyeContact":false,"instant":false,"magnitude":4,"progressive":false,"ranged":false,"resist":"","touch":true,"trigger":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"54926al16bxA6S13"}
{"name":"For to Cause the Conflagration of a hurtling Missle","permission":{"default":0,"5OXcsyHbucZmXIwZ":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":"<p>Casting this spell on a missile weapon, arrow, crossbow bolt, pistol/musket ball or cannonball will cause it to burst into flame when it strikes a target. When it hits a target, the missile will deal 1D10 points of magickal fire damage on top of its normal damage. A missile under the effects of For to Cause the Conflagration of a Hurtling Missile cannot benefit from For to Multiply a Hurtling Missile or For to Speed a Hurtling Missile.</p>","skill":"0","area":0,"charm":false,"concentration":false,"distant":false,"duration":1,"eyeContact":false,"instant":false,"magnitude":2,"progressive":false,"ranged":false,"resist":"","touch":true,"trigger":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"bLWDL541nMeGuLDQ"}
